üîπ 3Ô∏è‚É£ DAX Measures ‚Äì Core Sales KPIs
üìä Base Metrics
Total Sales = SUM ( Sales[Sales] )

Total Quantity = SUM ( Sales[Quantity] )

Total Profit = SUM ( Sales[Profit] )

Total Orders = DISTINCTCOUNT ( Sales[Order ID] )

üìà Performance Metrics
Average Order Value (AOV) =
DIVIDE ( [Total Sales], [Total Orders] )

Profit Margin (%) =
DIVIDE ( [Total Profit], [Total Sales] ) * 100

üè∑Ô∏è Discount & Pricing
Average Discount (%) =
AVERAGE ( Sales[Discount] ) * 100

Sales After Discount =
SUMX (
    Sales,
    Sales[Sales] * ( 1 - Sales[Discount] )
)

üìÖ Time-Based Metrics
Monthly Sales =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    ALLEXCEPT ( DateTable, DateTable[Year], DateTable[Month Number] )
)

Yearly Sales =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    ALLEXCEPT ( DateTable, DateTable[Year] )
)

üõçÔ∏è Product & Category Analysis
Sales by Category =
CALCULATE ( [Total Sales], VALUES ( Sales[Category] ) )

Top Product Sales =
CALCULATE (
    [Total Sales],
    TOPN ( 5, VALUES ( Sales[Product Name] ), [Total Sales], DESC )
)

üåç Regional Performance
